//TEXT
<jaT0001>Right. I remembered the two hand grenades I got from Ryota. It was a dangerous weapon that could catch us in the blast if I was one step off, but if we can't use our guns, it may be time for this.
<enT0001>Right. I remembered the two hand grenades I got from Ryota. It was a dangerous weapon that could catch us in the blast if I was one step off, but if we can't use our guns, it may be time for this.

//TEXT
<jaT0002>I gripping the lever of the grenade and pulled the safety pin. Then I looked at the man heading for us.
<enT0002>I gripping the lever of the grenade and pulled the safety pin. Then I looked at the man heading for us.

//TEXT
<jaT0003>He shouldn't be able to defend against the blast with that shield. If I time it right and it explodes point-blank, it should stop his assault.
<enT0003>He shouldn't be able to defend against the blast with that shield. If I time it right and it explodes point-blank, it should stop his assault.

//TEXT
<jaT0004>I carefully calculated the distance and checked to make sure all our members were behind cover. Alright. We're in a closed space, but if we have this much distance from the target, we should be safe.
<enT0004>I carefully calculated the distance and checked to make sure all our members were behind cover. Alright. We're in a closed space, but if we have this much distance from the target, we should be safe.

//TEXT
<jaT0005>I made sure there were no mistakes, and hurled the hand grenade in a straight arc to avoid the ceiling.
<enT0005>I made sure there were no mistakes, and hurled the hand grenade in a straight arc to avoid the ceiling.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0006>"Alright, everyone get down!"
<enT0006>"Alright, everyone get down!"

//TEXT
<jaT0007>I shouted, checked the target, and watched the grenade fly straight for the man. However...
<enT0007>I shouted, checked the target, and watched the grenade fly straight for the man. However...

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0008>"(Does he have some idea? He's not panicked at all.)"
<enT0008>"(Does he have some idea? He's not panicked at all.)"

//TEXT
<jaT0009>I had a bad feeling and a chill went down my spine. The next instant, my worry became reality.
<enT0009>I had a bad feeling and a chill went down my spine. The next instant, my worry became reality.

//TEXT
<jaT0010>The man suddenly ran for the hand grenade and thrust the shield in his left hand forward.
<enT0010>The man suddenly ran for the hand grenade and thrust the shield in his left hand forward.

//TEXT
<jaT0011>The next instant, the grenade hit the shield and rebounded with a thud, rolling along the ground back to us.
<enT0011>The next instant, the grenade hit the shield and rebounded with a thud, rolling along the ground back to us.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0012>"(That bastard!)"
<enT0012>"(That bastard!)"

//TEXT
<jaT0013>The hand grenade we used was originally theirs. He must have known the exact timing after lighting the fuse.
<enT0013>The hand grenade we used was originally theirs. He must have known the exact timing after lighting the fuse.

//TEXT
<jaT0014>That grenade, round like an apple, came cruelly rolling back to us.
<enT0014>That grenade, round like an apple, came cruelly rolling back to us.

//TEXT 【Shuhei】
<jaT0015>"(Shit! If it explodes at this range everyone will...)"
<enT0015>"(Shit! If it explodes at this range everyone will...)"

//TEXT
<jaT0016>Everyone had taken cover, so no one knew what had happened. I was the only one who could respond.
<enT0016>Everyone had taken cover, so no one knew what had happened. I was the only one who could respond.

//TEXT
<jaT0017>I automatically tried to cover the grenade. However...
<enT0017>I automatically tried to cover the grenade. However...

//TEXT
<jaT0018>The next instant my body was blown apart in the fierce explosion.
<enT0018>The next instant my body was blown apart in the fierce explosion.

//TEXT
<jaT0019>......
<enT0019>......

